{"tid":1535391,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！割霧丸有內鬼摷翻816英美港盟出嚟講，連登仔快啲推波助瀾一齊宣傳","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:56:23.000Z","uid":219269,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4489ad3da0568829050c47e3cf6b8efe39c8e6","tid":1535391,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"本來沉咗<br />\n而家用國家力量推翻上面<br />\n幫到咁明顯仲唔快啲share出去<br />\n連埋割霧丸段新聞一齊推出去<br />\n<br />\n為答謝国家級認證 #攬炒路線 ，我地決定送上「8.16 學界x攬炒萬人集會宣傳片」作為回禮！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jC-KG3nUGjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjC-KG3nUGjs&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5a281602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jC-KG3nUGjs</a><br />\n<br />\n高清版8.16場刊下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SJZRSs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SJZRSs&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5d64f214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SJZRSs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe shall NEVER surrender.<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港 #時代革命<br />\n#寧化飛灰 #不作浮塵"},{"pid":"21645b0509411f4396321d2d2c8d7c968749a71b","tid":1535391,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE